ActBritish Columbia Treaty Commission Act
PrecisRe-appointment of LISEANNE FORAND of North Saanich, British Columbia, as a Commissioner of the British Columbia Treaty Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of nine months, or until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first.
